{
  "stem": "6052.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And this kind of smoothed over what happened to my mother and sisters while they were alive in Leipzig and while the war was going on.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because we escaped, and our group was sent, in the war-- the war was already in full flare in 1939, and this was in the middle of the war, or in the beginning of the war, where our escape succeeded.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they were very worrisome about our fate and followed up what happened on the war zone.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the rescue continued, because the war was going on, and the-- they anticipated the bombardments which followed later, on Yugoslavia and the conquest of Yugoslavia.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And rightly so, because we were put together again on a certain day which I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I know it was not far away from Passover.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was 10 days or 12 days or 14 days before Passover.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We were put together and went from Zagreb to Belgrade, to reorganize-- I don't know the exact reason-- right to Belgrade.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But from Belgrade we could escape.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We were, again, called, each one by a messenger, to where we were called to come to the rail station and to go from there to a place we did not know.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At that point, we felt already that some things were going on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But again, as youngster we did-- youngsters, we did not feel the full strength, the full force, of a war which was raging already strongly.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we became more-- the aware-- the awareness, for me, at least-- and I was the oldest.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My brother is two and a half years younger-- was quite clear.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That something-- that things, bad things, are happening.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And at that time, don't forget, my mother was-- my mother and sisters and all were still alive.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
